<author>bhjt ʿdly, bhjt ʿdly</author>
<title>fwq ạlṣlyb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- fwq ạlṣlyb mnẓr ʿjyb .. wạldm nạzf fwq ạlṣlyb
 lyh yạ ḥbyyb wạldyn rhyb .. tḥml ʿqạby lyh yạ ḥbyb
 ạlqrạr- yạ ạ̉brʿ jmạl fwq ạlṣlyb .. lạ ṣwrẗ lyk wlạ jmạl
 fyn ạljmạl .. fyã ạ̉nạ .. ạ̹zạy ạ̉nạ
 2- ạ̉nạ ạlạ̉tẖym dẖnby ʿẓym .. wqlby kẖạdʿ wạnt ạlrḥym
 ḥbk ḥmym dmk krym .. wạlṣlb qạsy wạlmwt ạ̉lym</lyrics>
</song>